=Episode 9=

14
00:01:00,760 --> 00:01:01,600
Father.

15
00:01:03,600 --> 00:01:04,440
Anran.

16
00:01:04,560 --> 00:01:05,400
Father.

17
00:01:05,800 --> 00:01:06,960
- Why are you beaten?
- Sit.

18
00:01:07,000 --> 00:01:08,800
Who did this? Was it Helian Zheng?

19
00:01:08,960 --> 00:01:09,880
No, no, no.

20
00:01:10,060 --> 00:01:10,950
It wasn't He Zheng.

21
00:01:10,960 --> 00:01:12,240
It was He Zheng who saved me.

22
00:01:14,160 --> 00:01:15,360
The situation is urgent.

23
00:01:15,480 --> 00:01:16,400
Listen,

24
00:01:17,080 --> 00:01:18,800
there's a man named Li Yang.

25
00:01:19,400 --> 00:01:22,280
He secretly arranged
the bandit job for me.

26
00:01:23,680 --> 00:01:25,040
Father, don't worry.

27
00:01:25,200 --> 00:01:26,440
I will definitely find him.

28
00:01:26,560 --> 00:01:27,400
Okay.

29
00:01:27,520 --> 00:01:28,360
By the way, father,

30
00:01:28,680 --> 00:01:29,560
Ming'an is back.

31
00:01:29,840 --> 00:01:31,760
We have one more person to help us out.

32
00:01:36,440 --> 00:01:37,800
I've always been an honest,

33
00:01:37,880 --> 00:01:39,360
and law-abiding businessman.

34
00:01:40,720 --> 00:01:42,560
I've never harmed anyone.

35
00:01:42,880 --> 00:01:43,800
The only mistake

36
00:01:44,040 --> 00:01:45,280
was trusting the wrong person.

37
00:01:46,560 --> 00:01:48,680
It's karma, karma...

38
00:01:49,080 --> 00:01:51,360
Father, as long as we do the right thing,

39
00:01:51,760 --> 00:01:53,080
