40
00:01:56,440 --> 00:01:57,280
How about you?

41
00:01:58,200 --> 00:01:59,580
Did He Zheng give you a hard time?

42
00:02:00,000 --> 00:02:01,560
It's all my fault.

43
00:02:02,480 --> 00:02:03,720
He won't do anything to me.

44
00:02:04,040 --> 00:02:05,520
He still wants the gold mine.

45
00:02:07,960 --> 00:02:09,760
You two are siblings.

46
00:02:10,000 --> 00:02:11,400
How can you get married?

47
00:02:11,840 --> 00:02:13,360
This is just ridiculous.

48
00:02:13,520 --> 00:02:15,520
Father, I need to ask you something.

49
00:02:16,440 --> 00:02:17,880
Why did Concubine Liang

50
00:02:17,960 --> 00:02:19,000
commit suicide?

51
00:02:19,400 --> 00:02:20,840
Brother believes it's related to you.

52
00:02:22,160 --> 00:02:24,080
This woman betrayed the He Family.

53
00:02:24,800 --> 00:02:26,440
She wronged us.

54
00:02:27,240 --> 00:02:29,160
He Zheng came to seek revenge on us.

55
00:02:29,440 --> 00:02:30,600
You must trust me.

56
00:02:33,400 --> 00:02:34,360
Of course, I trust you.

57
00:02:36,080 --> 00:02:36,920
By the way, father,

58
00:02:37,280 --> 00:02:39,040
I have found the dowry you gave me.

59
00:02:39,280 --> 00:02:40,400
- Good.
- Don't worry.

60
00:02:40,520 --> 00:02:42,200
I will use it well.

61
00:02:42,400 --> 00:02:43,560
I'll protect you.

62
00:02:47,960 --> 00:02:48,800
Good.

63
00:03:44,760 --> 00:03:45,600
Zheng.

64
00:03:46,720 --> 00:03:47,560
Why are you here?

65
00:03:48,800 --> 00:03:49,880
Why didn't you call me?

66
00:03:51,000 --> 00:03:52,120
Thank you for the address

67
00:03:52,280 --> 00:03:53,760
you gave me the other day,

68
00:03:54,120 --> 00:03:55,280
and for the small gift.

69
00:03:57,920 --> 00:03:58,760
Tang.

70
00:03:59,560 --> 00:04:00,680
Your outfit

71
00:04:00,840 --> 00:04:02,520
is quite unique.

72
00:04:03,640 --> 00:04:05,040
You've brought me some wine.

73
00:04:06,080 --> 00:04:07,440
Why bother making the trip?

74
00:04:08,040 --> 00:04:09,640
Didn't I finish your precious wine

75
00:04:09,640 --> 00:04:10,360
the other day?

76
00:04:10,920 --> 00:04:13,000
So I brought two bottles of imported liquor.

77
00:04:14,520 --> 00:04:15,360
By the way,

78
00:04:15,720 --> 00:04:17,360
visit my mansion someday.

79
00:04:17,840 --> 00:04:19,080
Take a look at my new home.

80
00:04:19,880 --> 00:04:20,720
Zheng.

81
00:04:21,720 --> 00:04:23,280
Haven't heard me perform yet, right?

82
00:04:24,560 --> 00:04:25,400
How about

83
00:04:26,120 --> 00:04:28,680
I sing you a piece for you.

84
00:04:30,120 --> 00:04:30,960
Great.

85
00:04:31,400 --> 00:04:32,320
I'm all ears.

86
00:04:50,880 --> 00:04:55,640
♪In the dark night, I fell into your eyes♪

87
00:04:57,600 --> 00:05:00,920
♪A spark deeply buried in the first dream♪

88
00:05:00,930 --> 00:05:02,320
Look, this stroke here

89
00:05:03,120 --> 00:05:04,520
